\n河套條界俾政府偷偷改過, 改少左香港範圍</blockquote><br />\n海域空域都有，造成香港海運衰落，深圳用香港97年嘅海域填海<br />\n空域割讓亦制約香港機場發展<br />\n不過河套係大陸用黎突破64後西方對中國輸入高科技嘅制裁"},{"pid":"8086d59e8bdf0dd2a590e7f750128adfdc8ceeda","tid":92820,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等睇港豬出雞棚蝗出滴豉油，到最後雞油都冇得港豬食！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有名你叫架啦：河蟹套路區！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d18c4df95f6c56c35e210fa81e7f9eaf082c6c42","tid":92820,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">失？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你幾撚時有過話事權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8f5f09a56f6e96cdfc3c9148767ceb523fb02f","tid":92820,"uid":49678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"等睇港奸全力配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513ca3f2cca63033ae5329691937310b0aa22bbf","tid":92820,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:30:18.000Z","msg":"港方將提名四名（包括主席）、深方提名三名，餘下三名由兩方共同提名<br />\n<br />\n香港佔四個, 其中一個係主席<br />\n大陸佔三個<br />\n<br />\n剩番三個是雙方提名, 但由於香港與大陸是 4:3, 所以香港可以食哂剩番果三個位<br />\n<br />\n最終結果是:<br />\n香港 佔7個, 其中一個是主席<br />\n大陸 佔3個<br />\n<br />\n點計都係香港人話哂事"},{"pid":"fee8a63b7f42d3f3900d9d7e224b9b61a83c882e","tid":92820,"uid":39733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"根本就係㩒住香港嚟搶"},{"pid":"d8488a9c615668b0d0d6f3fe18e